Description: Beyondcell computes a score summarizing the cell-based drug
    sensitivity for each cell in your experiment and a subset of drugs of
    interest. It also includes functions to prioritize drugs based on
    these scores and visualize the results.
License: GPL-2
URL: https://github.com/cnio-bu/beyondcell,
    https://bioinformatics.cnio.es/tools/
BugReports: https://github.com/cnio-bu/beyondcell/issues
